node.text:
Hairstyle 1:
Hairspray @oribe
Dry shampoo @garnierusa 
Hair pins & scrunchie @mykitsch x @justinemarjan (some of these styles were inspired by Justine :)
Hairstyle 2: water bottle from @amazon (I talked about it in my first Amazon favorites video)
Hairspray #oribehair
Hairpin a gift from @pixibeauty
@agaveoil straightener
Hair brush: @sprnettehairbrushes 
Hairstyle 3: I used black eyeshadow to cover my gray hair LOL
Rhinestones from @hobbylobby
I used @duoadhesive lash glue for the Rhinestones you can also use hair glue if you have it on hand. The only lash glue I recommend using is the duo in the tube that dries clear, it washes right out the hair. The Duo lash glue In a bottle with a brush will not wash out of your hair  easily 💁‍♀️
Thank you so much for watching 💕
#hairstyles #hairstyle #hair #hairtransformation
